page_title: How to work with prompt engineering and the Chat Completion API
page_description: Learn how to work with the Chat Completion API for prompt engineering.
chunk_content: Repeat instructions at the endModels can be susceptible to recency bias, which in this context means that information at the end of the prompt might have more significant influence over the output than information at the beginning of the prompt. Therefore, it's worth experimenting with repeating the instructions at the end of the prompt and evaluating the impact on the generated response.
